A fixed-rate exchange in which Bitcoins may be purchased by way of an SMS text message.

The list of countries where this service is available is:

* Austria
* Belgium
* Bulgaria
* Canada
* Croatia
* Denmark
* Estonia
* Finland
* France
* Germany (Deutschland)
* Hungary
* Ireland
* Italy
* Lithuania
* Luxembourg
* Montenegro
* Netherlands
* Norway
* Portugal
* Slovakia
* Spain
* Sweden
* Switzerland
* United Kingdom

Payment for the purchase is made through the mobile service.

##History

The service was launched on August 23, 2011 (2.1). 

On July 4, 2012 BTC-Direct announced to stop offering Bitcoins (2.2).

